    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/efc8eefb592a6c4f94f43280351e9abe.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/48a376a63944aab41b3530eb2d79a5fe.poster.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/48a376a63944aab41b3530eb2d79a5fe.webm?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/48a376a63944aab41b3530eb2d79a5fe.mp4?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《岚：外传》是一款融合快节奏斩击的回合制动作游戏。利用冲刺机制迅速穿梭关卡，帅气地将敌人一分为二！结合手中之刃、手里剑、瞬移与锁链，碾碎你的对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/998fb40fdee593fbc3e10c401683cc81.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关中独特的机制将彻底改变你的操作方式，而Boss战更将颠覆你对“回合制”的想像！他们将实时释放技能，考验你的临场应变！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 冻结敌人的时间、投出手里剑、瞬间位移，甚至改变冲刺方向！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/67276cb4d47b7caaa7a29f93143811f6.poster.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/67276cb4d47b7caaa7a29f93143811f6.webm?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/67276cb4d47b7caaa7a29f93143811f6.mp4?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放强大忍术，掌控战场节奏，打出华丽连招，用创意赢得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7位Boss同样打破回合节奏，使用炸弹、陷阱、飞斩、火焰等招式袭来！谨慎应对，或疯狂猛攻，一切由你决定。 !!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/dcb92bf5052b85b5b585b7158f23d9d3.poster.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/dcb92bf5052b85b5b585b7158f23d9d3.webm?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/dcb92bf5052b85b5b585b7158f23d9d3.mp4?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过5小时内容丰富的回合制战斗，关卡设计多样，解法自由，挑战你的智与勇！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新定义的战斗系统，冲刺&amp;砍杀机制，享受兼具速度感的回合制动作体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款拥有解谜元素的风格化回合动作游戏（或是一款拥有战斗元素的解谜游戏）！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/91ddd2211e150a9f53690308e3cf03f8.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/d1c87e927e65cd5371621deeacaf1ae9.poster.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/d1c87e927e65cd5371621deeacaf1ae9.webm?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/d1c87e927e65cd5371621deeacaf1ae9.mp4?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关过程中可解锁多种强化技能，但在战斗中如何运用，完全取决于你！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个房间中追求完美评分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新技能后，重新挑战关卡，体验全新战斗方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在像素艺术打造的美丽场景中挥斩敌人，血肉横飞、爽感拉满，舞台灵感来自日本各地。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开岚的过去、他与“狼”的牵连，并进一步了解Bravery宇宙的深层世界观。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/08bedec3af0b1e09e9454bd09973c8dc.poster.avif?t=1752894099\" width=770 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/08bedec3af0b1e09e9454bd09973c8dc.webm?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040170/extras/08bedec3af0b1e09e9454bd09973c8dc.mp4?t=1752894099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
